  "synopsis": "He starts with a mountain stronghold and two members (a strategist and a groom), determined to build the strongest stronghold. He transmigrates to a chaotic world, owning a stronghold on the verge of collapse. Faced with this bloody and chaotic world, will he rob money, food, and women to become a carefree mountain king, or will he spill his blood, clash with the heroes of the world, and fight for a name that will resonate throughout history, asking: Are kings and generals born with a special destiny?\n\n(Source: Tencent, translated)",
